Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_br_rx::_eer

GSER software BASE-R RX link training equalization evaluation request (EER). A write to [RXT_EER] initiates a equalization request to the RAW PCS. A read of this register returns the equalization status message and a valid bit indicating it was updated. These registers are for diagnostic use only.
